# data splitting
library(caret)
set.seed(353)
# 
trainIndex <- createDataPartition(temp_train$Survived, p = .8, 
                                  list = FALSE, 
                                  times = 1)
#head(trainIndex)
# 
temp_tr = temp_train %>% 
  slice(trainIndex)
# 
temp_te = temp_train %>% 
  slice(-trainIndex)

  datatable()

Using caret to do

# 
fitControl <- trainControl(method="repeatedcv",
                            number = 10, # threshold for pca preprocess
                            repeats = 5,
                            classProbs = TRUE,
                            summaryFunction = twoClassSummary)
# LDA get
model_lda <- train(Survived ~.,
                       temp_tr,
                       method="lda",
                       #tuneLength = 10,
                       metric="ROC",
                       preProc = c("center", "scale"),
                       trControl=fitControl)
# 
pred_lda <- predict(model_lda,temp_te[,-1])
# confusion matrix
cm_lda <- confusionMatrix(pred_lda, temp_te$Survived, positive = "X1")
